Sentencas: In this study, influence of carbon impurities on characteristics of ALD-YSZ films is systematically investigated.
Titulo: Effects of carbon contaminations on Y2O3-stabilized ZrO2 thin film electrolyte prepared by atomic layer deposition for thin film solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Carbon concentration in ALD-YSZ films was controlled by changing Y2O3 ratio in YSZ super cycle.
Titulo: Effects of carbon contaminations on Y2O3-stabilized ZrO2 thin film electrolyte prepared by atomic layer deposition for thin film solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: To examine electrochemical characteristics of ALD-YSZ films, nano-porous templates based thin film solid oxide fuel cells (TF-SOFCs) were fabricated with ALD-YSZ thin film electrolyte and examined at 500 degrees C. Open circuit voltages (OCVs) of TF-SOFCs with ALD-YSZ were clearly dependent on carbon contaminations.
Titulo: Effects of carbon contaminations on Y2O3-stabilized ZrO2 thin film electrolyte prepared by atomic layer deposition for thin film solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: High carbon concentration caused leakage current through internal short circuit, and then, OCVs of TF-SOFCs were decreased.
Titulo: Effects of carbon contaminations on Y2O3-stabilized ZrO2 thin film electrolyte prepared by atomic layer deposition for thin film solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Post-processing of ALD-YSZ thin film electrolyte improved OCVs of TF-SOFCs.
Titulo: Effects of carbon contaminations on Y2O3-stabilized ZrO2 thin film electrolyte prepared by atomic layer deposition for thin film solid oxide fuel cells
